同時，<br />\n她也失去了權力以外的所有東西<br />\n<br />\n回到空蕩蕩的家，<br />\n月娥在餐桌上獨自一人吃著晚餐</span></span>"},{"pid":"5c8f08811ff30d63db35bb84ad229693dab89e4c","tid":1238930,"uid":127751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"佢老公唯一一個已經證實中出過林奠(2次)既人"},{"pid":"8041b7e175607d060dec7e8e0a7ca1ddbb4110bc","tid":1238930,"uid":127751,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/n3LRdPf2l5A/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fn3LRdPf2l5A%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=481ab569&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fb7dab01b5f1d323e2c99c5318f65050fa8b774","tid":1238930,"uid":27415,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8041b7e175607d060dec7e8e0a7ca1ddbb4110bc","tid":1238930,"uid":127751,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/n3LRdPf2l5A/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fn3LRdPf2l5A%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=481ab569&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"吃過晚飯洗了澡，月娥愜意地躺在床上<br />\n今早丈夫說有飯聚晚點才回家，她卻鬆了一口氣<br />\n她倆在劍橋讀書時認識<br />\n本來是感情很好的兩小無猜<br />\n卻在婚後行房才發現丈夫是林早洩<br />\n雖然無礙生育，但卻一直令她對和丈夫做愛這回事感到意興闌珊<br />\n振英和他不同，鞭鞭有力<br />\n工作時深藏不露，<br />\n在床上則如一匹荒野中的狼<br />\n想到這裡，月娥的心又是一陣悸動<br />\n<br />\n突然手機傳來震動，一看原來是振英的短訊<br />\n「想我了嗎? 你的加藤英上」<br />\n<br />\n月娥笑了，這是振英自稱的綽號，因為他說他也有讓女人欲仙欲死的金手指<br />\n<br />\n「叮咚--」正想回覆之際，家裡的門鈴響了"},{"pid":"c0ac8169b9ed25ee897508beb113f05dcac14171","tid":1238930,"uid":9115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"83069b8bf6655a77bb186902650ea916e267b00e","tid":1238930,"uid":35296,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"quote":{"pid":"fbf48f0fe38fb0f688f637640ecf56c0f8cde974","tid":1238930,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:19:17.000Z","msg":"召喚林鄭選舉咸濕文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi